Transport or losses are logically not relevant for this type of products.;This is the market for  'wood preservation facility, vacuum pressure method', in the Global geography.;This market contains no transport or losses, as they are irrelevant for the delivered product.;This is an immobile infrastructure, representing the construction of wood preservation facility used for vacuum pressure method. It has a yearly output of 6,000 m3 timber, a life time of 50 years and a life time output of 450,000 m3 treated timber. The process includes land use, all materials necessary to construct it, their decommission and strorage. 

This activity starts with the built infrastructure ready to use.

This activity ends with the infrastructure made accessible to the users. Transport or losses are considered irrelevant for this product.
